ran for office, he said that by this year</div></div><div data-time="3322.62" class="caption-line" id="cp-810"><div class="caption-line-time">55:22</div><div class="caption-line-text">he would have brought down the cost of insurance
for each family by $2,500 a family. Instead,</div></div><div data-time="3328.13" class="caption-line" id="cp-811"><div class="caption-line-time">55:28</div><div class="caption-line-text">it's gone up by that amount. So it's expensive.
Expensive things hurt families. So that's</div></div><div data-time="3333.46" class="caption-line" id="cp-812"><div class="caption-line-time">55:33</div><div class="caption-line-text">one reason I don't want it.</div></div><div data-time="3334.94" class="caption-line" id="cp-813"><div class="caption-line-time">55:34</div><div class="caption-line-text">Second reason, it cuts $716 billion from Medicare
to pay for it. I want to put that money back</div></div><div data-time="3340.65" class="caption-line" id="cp-814"><div class="caption-line-time">55:40</div><div class="caption-line-text">in Medicare for our seniors.</div></div><div data-time="3342.69" class="caption-line" id="cp-815"><div class="caption-line-time">55:42</div><div class="caption-line-text">Number three, it puts in place an unelected
board that's going to tell people, ultimately,</div></div><div data-time="3347.37" class="caption-line" id="cp-816"><div class="caption-line-time">55:47</div><div class="caption-line-text">what kind of treatments they can have. I don't
like that idea.</div></div><div data-time="3350.83" class="caption-line" id="cp-817"><div class="caption-line-time">55:50</div><div class="caption-line-text">Fourth, there was a survey done of small businesses
across the country. It said, what's been the</div></div><div data-time="3356.45" class="caption-line" id="cp-818"><div class="caption-line-time">55:56</div><div class="caption-line-text">effect of "Obamacare" on your hiring plans?
And three-quarters of them said, it makes</div></div><div data-time="3360.81" class="caption-line" id="cp-819"><div class="caption-line-time">56:00</div><div class="caption-line-text">us less likely to hire people. I just don't
know how the president could have come into</div></div><div data-time="3366.5" class="caption-line" id="cp-820"><div class="caption-line-time">56:06</div><div class="caption-line-text">office, facing 23 million people out of work,
rising unemployment, an economic crisis at</div></div><div data-time="3371.87" class="caption-line" id="cp-821"><div class="caption-line-time">56:11</div><div class="caption-line-text">the — at the kitchen table and spent his
energy and passion for two years fighting</div></div><div data-time="3375.93" class="caption-line" id="cp-822"><div class="caption-line-time">56:15</div><div class="caption-line-text">for "Obamacare" instead of fighting for jobs
for the American people.</div></div><div data-time="3379.95" class="caption-line" id="cp-823"><div class="caption-line-time">56:19</div><div class="caption-line-text">It has killed jobs. And the best course for
