spending more on administrative costs and</div></div><div data-time="3497.95" class="caption-line" id="cp-847"><div class="caption-line-time">58:17</div><div class="caption-line-text">profits than they are on actual care.</div></div><div data-time="3501.11" class="caption-line" id="cp-848"><div class="caption-line-time">58:21</div><div class="caption-line-text">Number two, if you don't have health insurance,
