of health care experts, doctors, et cetera,</div></div><div data-time="3733.21" class="caption-line" id="cp-907"><div class="caption-line-time">62:13</div><div class="caption-line-text">to figure out how can we reduce the cost of
care in the system overall, because the — there</div></div><div data-time="3741.84" class="caption-line" id="cp-908"><div class="caption-line-time">62:21</div><div class="caption-line-text">are two ways of dealing with our health care
crisis.</div></div><div data-time="3745.66" class="caption-line" id="cp-909"><div class="caption-line-time">62:25</div><div class="caption-line-text">One is to simply leave a whole bunch of people
