also some things we do better together.</div></div><div data-time="4347.53" class="caption-line" id="cp-1038"><div class="caption-line-time">72:27</div><div class="caption-line-text">So in the middle of the Civil War, Abraham
Lincoln said, let's help to finance the Transcontinental</div></div><div data-time="4353.469" class="caption-line" id="cp-1039"><div class="caption-line-time">72:33</div><div class="caption-line-text">Railroad. Let's start the National Academy
