opportunity for all Americans, because if</div></div><div data-time="4368.289" class="caption-line" id="cp-1041"><div class="caption-line-time">72:48</div><div class="caption-line-text">all Americans are getting opportunity, we're
all going to be better off. That doesn't restrict</div></div><div data-time="4372.46" class="caption-line" id="cp-1042"><div class="caption-line-time">72:52</div><div class="caption-line-text">people's freedom; that enhances it.</div></div><div data-time="4375.639" class="caption-line" id="cp-1043"><div class="caption-line-time">72:55</div><div class="caption-line-text">And so what I've tried to do as president
is to apply those same principles. And when</div></div><div data-time="4381.469" class="caption-line" id="cp-1044"><div class="caption-line-time">73:01</div><div class="caption-line-text">it comes to education, what I've said is we've
got to reform schools that are not working.</div></div><div data-time="4386.989" class="caption-line" id="cp-1045"><div class="caption-line-time">73:06</div><div class="caption-line-text">We use something called Race to the Top. Wasn't
